{"word":"αἴγλη","slug":"αἴγλη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n2181\" key=\"ai)/glh\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">αἴγλη</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <sense id=\"n2181.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the light of the sun</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">moon</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:45\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.45</biblScope></bibl>, etc.:—of the radiance of Olympus, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λευκὴ αἴ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:6:45\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.45</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg002.perseus-grc1:610\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ant.\">Ant.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">610</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἰς αἴγλαν μολεῖν</foreign> to come to <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">daylight</tr_>, i.e. to be born, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg003.perseus-grc1:1:35\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">N.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.35</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">φοιβὰν ὑπαὶ χειμῶνος αἴ.</foreign>, of <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">sunshine</tr_> on edge of storm-cloud, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0199.tlg001:12:140\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ B.\">B.</